           <a href="#"><input type="text" value="" readonly="" class="inp-box sel" name="bank"  ></a>
     </div>
     <div class="inp-div">
           <span class="inp-span mi">房产证号</span><span class="inp-r">&nbsp;</span>
           <input type="text" value=""  class="inp-box" name="bank3" placeholder="请输入">
     </div>
	   <div class="inp-div no-border">
           <span class="inp-span mi">姓名/身份证</span><span class="inp-r"></span>
           <input type="text" value=""  class="inp-box" name="bank3" placeholder="请输入">
     </div>
	 
	 <div class="clear" > </div>
</div>

<div class="clear" style="height:10px;"> </div>
<div class="sub-but dis">查询</div> 

<p class="tit-p">查询结果 (此结果来自深圳市房地产信息系统)</p>
<p class="detail-p">查询时间：<span>2017-05-21 22:56 </span><br>

